OL,3,C'Bittersweet' moment for family as man
OL,4,Csentenced for killing former partner
OL,6,FThe family of a mother-of-four killed
OL,7,Fby her former partner have described
OL,8,Fthe sentencing of her murderer as
OL,9,F"bittersweet".JWilliam Finlay, 68, of
OL,10,FOld Forde Gardens in Whitehead,
OL,11,Fpleaded guilty last year to murdering
OL,12,F64-year-old Alyson Nelson at her home
OL,13,Fin Victoria Avenue in the Co Antrim
OL,14,Ftown.JThe victim was described at
OL,15,FBelfast Crown Court as a "beloved
OL,16,Fmother and grandmother" who, her
OL,17,Ffamily said, was "constantly bubbling
OL,18,Fwith life".
