OL,6,FThe conviction is the first in
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland to be aggravated by
OL,8,Fdomestic abuse. The judge, who had
OL,9,Fpreviously imposed a life sentence on
OL,10,FFinlay, told him he would serve a
OL,11,Fminimum of 20 years before he could be
OL,12,Fconsidered for release.
